This example is partially based on a blog post "Running Solr with Maven", by Petri Kainulainen:
http://www.petrikainulainen.net/programming/maven/running-solr-with-maven/

* for running the Solr webapplication module:
>> cd solr-webapp
>> mvn jetty:run

* open browser and go to url: http://localhost:8983/solr/
